ss=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4\">Real People, Real Results</h2><p class=\"text-muted-foreground text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Hear from users who have transformed their businesses and lives with PostAll.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border h-full flex flex-col\"><div class=\"bg-emerald-500 p-6 text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-full bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-lg font-bold\">AO</span></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg\">Adebayo Ogunleye</h3><p class=\"text-white/80 text-sm\">Electronics Seller<!-- --> • <!-- -->Lagos</p></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium w-fit whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive transition-[color,box-shadow] overflow-hidden border-transparent [a&amp;]:hover:bg-primary/90 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target h-3 w-3 mr-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>From zero online presence to ₦500K monthly revenue</span></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote h-5 w-5 text-emerald-300 mb-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed flex-1 italic\">“<!-- -->Before PostAll, I was struggling to find customers beyond my immediate neighborhood. I signed up, listed my products with good photos, and within the first week, I had 15 orders. The escrow system made buyers trust me instantly. Now I fulfill 50+ orders monthly and have even hired an assistant. PostAll didn&#x27;t just give me customers — it gave me a real business.<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-4 w-4 text-emerald-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400\">Key Metric: <!-- -->₦500K/mo</span></div></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border h-full flex flex-col\"><div class=\"bg-emerald-600 p-6 text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-full bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-lg font-bold\">CN</span></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg\">Chioma Nwosu</h3><p class=\"text-white/80 text-sm\">Homeowner<!-- --> • <!-- -->Abuja</p></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium w-fit whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive transition-[color,box-shadow] overflow-hidden border-transparent [a&amp;]:hover:bg-primary/90 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target h-3 w-3 mr-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>Found dream apartment in 2 days</span></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote h-5 w-5 text-emerald-300 mb-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed flex-1 italic\">“<!-- -->I had been searching for a 3-bedroom apartment in Garki for months with no luck. A friend suggested I check PostAll. Within 2 days, I found a beautiful apartment listed by a verified agent. The safe meeting spot feature made the inspection stress-free, and the agent was professional. I signed the lease the following week. I also saved ₦150K compared to agency fees I was quoted elsewhere.<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-4 w-4 text-emerald-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400\">Key Metric: <!-- -->2 days</span></div></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground gap-6 rounded-xl py-6 shadow-sm overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border h-full flex flex-col\"><div class=\"bg-teal-600 p-6 text-white\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4\"><div class=\"h-14 w-14 rounded-full bg-white/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\"><span class=\"text-lg font-bold\">ET</span></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-lg\">Emeka Thompson</h3><p class=\"text-white/80 text-sm\">Web Developer<!-- --> • <!-- -->Lagos</p></div></div></div><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-6 flex-1 flex flex-col\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium w-fit whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive transition-[color,box-shadow] overflow-hidden border-transparent [a&amp;]:hover:bg-primary/90 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-400\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-target h-3 w-3 mr-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"6\"></circle><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg>Got hired for 15 projects in 3 months</span></div><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-quote h-5 w-5 text-emerald-300 mb-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path><path d=\"M5 3a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v6a2 2 0 0 0 2 2 1 1 0 0 1 1 1v1a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 1 1 0 0 0-1 1v2a1 1 0 0 0 1 1 6 6 0 0 0 6-6V5a2 2 0 0 0-2-2z\"></path></svg><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed flex-1 italic\">“<!-- -->As a freelance developer, finding consistent clients was my biggest challenge. PostAll changed everything. I created a profile, uploaded my portfolio, and started getting job matches immediately. In my first 3 months, I completed 15 projects with zero payment issues thanks to escrow. I now earn ₦350K monthly and have turned down offers from agencies. PostAll gave me the freedom to work on my own terms.<!-- -->”</p><div class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-4 w-4 text-emerald-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400\">Key Metric: <!-- -->15 projects</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"container mx-auto px-4 py-16 md:py-24\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><p class=\"text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground uppercase tracking-wider mb-6\">As Seen On</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 md:gap-10\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-muted/60 hover:bg-muted rounded-xl px-6 py-4 transition-colors\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-muted-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground\">TC</span></div><span class=\"font-semibold text-muted-foreground\">TechCabal</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-muted/60 hover:bg-muted rounded-xl px-6 py-4 transition-colors\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-muted-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground\">DA</span></div><span class=\"font-semibold text-muted-foreground\">Disrupt Africa</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-muted/60 hover:bg-muted rounded-xl px-6 py-4 transition-colors\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-muted-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground\">GN</span></div><span class=\"font-semibold text-muted-foreground\">Guardian Nigeria</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-muted/60 hover:bg-muted rounded-xl px-6 py-4 transition-colors\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-muted-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground\">PN</span></div><span class=\"font-semibold text-muted-foreground\">Pulse Nigeria</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 bg-muted/60 hover:bg-muted rounded-xl px-6 py-4 transition-colors\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-muted-foreground/10 flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-xs font-bold text-muted-foreground\">VA</span></div><span class=\"font-semibold text-muted-foreground\">Ventures Africa</span></div></div></div></section><section class=\"bg-muted/40 py-16 md:py-24\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"text-center mb-12\"><span data-slot=\"badge\" class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium w-fit whitespace-nowrap shrink-0 [&amp;&gt;svg]:size-3 gap-1 [&amp;&gt;svg]:pointer-events-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 focus-visible:ring-[3px] aria-invalid:ring-destructive/20 dark:aria-invalid:ring-destructive/40 aria-invalid:border-destructive transition-[color,box-shadow] overflow-hidden border-transparent [a&amp;]:hover:bg-secondary/90 bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-400 mb-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-message-circle h-3.5 w-3.5 mr-1.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M7.9 20A9 9 0 1 0 4 16.1L2 22Z\"></path></svg>Community</span><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4\">Community Highlights</h2><p class=\"text-muted-foreground text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Recent achievements and milestones from the PostAll community.</p></div><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"bg-card text-card-foreground flex flex-col gap-6 rounded-xl border py-6 shadow-sm\"><div data-slot=\"card-content\" class=\"p-0\"><div class=\"divide-y\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4 p-5 hover:bg-muted/50 transition-colors\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-lg bg-muted flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.